fields.name: Greek Yogurt
fields.description: Greek yogurt is a thicker, creamier version of regular yogurt. It’s made by straining out the whey, which is the liquid part of milk. This process gives Greek yogurt its rich texture, high protein content, and lower sugar compared to regular yogurt.
fields.composition: High in protein – helps in muscle repair and satiety  Low in sugar – better for diabetics  Contains probiotics – supports gut health  Rich in calcium & B12 – good for bones and energy

fields.name: pure paneer
fields.description: Paneer is a fresh, non-aged, non-melting Indian cheese made by curdling hot milk with a food acid like lemon juice, vinegar, or citric acid. It is a staple in Indian cuisine, especially vegetarian dishes, and is known for its mild flavor, soft yet firm texture, and high protein content.
fields.composition: Calories	260–320 kcal Protein	18–21 grams Fat	20–25 grams → Saturated Fat	13–17 grams Carbohydrates	1–2 grams

fields.name: Strawberry flavoured milk
fields.description: Flavoured milk is a sweetened dairy beverage made by adding natural  sugar or sweeteners. Common flavors include chocolate, strawberry, vanilla, mango, and cardamom
fields.composition: Calories	70–90 kcal Protein	3.0–3.5 grams Fat	1.0–3.5 grams (based on fat content of milk used) Carbohydrates	10–14 grams → Sugars (natural + added)	9–12 grams Calcium	100–130 mg

fields.name: vitamin D fortified milk
fields.description: Vitamin D fortified milk is regular milk that has vitamin D added to it to help prevent deficiency and support bone health. Since natural vitamin D content in milk is very low, fortification makes it a valuable source of this essential nutrient.
fields.composition: Calories	60–70 kcal Protein	3.2–3.4 grams Fat	3.2–3.5 grams (whole milk) / 1.5g (low-fat) Carbohydrates	4.8–5.0 grams → Sugars (Lactose)	~4.8 grams Calcium	120–130 mg Vitamin D (Fortified)	100 IU (2.5 µg)

fields.name: Cheddar cheese
fields.description: Indulge in the rich, tangy flavor of Lush Dairy’s Cheddar Cheese, crafted with care from the freshest cow’s milk. Aged to perfection, our cheddar offers a smooth, creamy texture with a bold, nutty taste that intensifies over time. Ideal for sandwiches, burgers, pastas, or cheese platters, it's the perfect addition to any meal. No description available.
